column2: what is i-venture?
column3: {'query': 'what is i-venture?', 'result': ' I-Venture is an entrepreneurial organization located at ISB that aims to foster entrepreneurship and nurture startups by providing them with resources and support under one roof. It also runs programs such as I-Win and OfExperiences to help professionals undergoing career transitions. Saumita, an ME and PhD in Biotechnology, is an alumnus of BITS Pilani and IIT Kharagpur and is involved in the organization. ', 'source_documents': [Document(page_content='- I-Venture @ ISB\n- one roof with an aim to foster entrepreneurship and nurture startups.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_category_startup-stories.txt'}), Document(page_content='Lami.Fit (lami.fit) is the perfect example of what happens when intuition, knowledge, experience and technology come together. The first-of-its-kind healthtech platform that uses DNA, and blood & body markers to predict health risks, Lami.fit synthesises the findings to curate personalised health plans that can prevent and reverse lifestyle diseases like diabetes, thyroid, PCOS, heart risks & chronic gut disorders.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_i-win-startup-stories-in-a-world-where-fitness-is-measured-by-weight-alone-lami-fit-stands-out-by-a-mile.txt'}), Document(page_content='We are an entrepreneurial company and we care about one thing above all, building value for the company and our customers. As an entrepreneurial organization we should always consider ourselves a team and work as one.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/local_file18_no_empty_lines.txt'}), Document(page_content='Monk & Mei, I-Win program', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_i-win-startup-stories-what-led-sonia-khatri-anand-to-build-a-global-brand-from-the-brink-of-shutdown.txt'}), Document(page_content='That is what led to the genesis of OfExperiences, a platform that builds, develops and equips professionals who are undergoing career transitions by running niche cohort-based programs for them across career stages, and providing them with relevant information, personalized guidance, and real connections to help them navigate through their transitional phase. OFExperiences also acts as a bridge between such professionals and organizations that are looking for similar talent. Not only does Lochan’s brainchild help organizations with ready talent, but they also provide valuable behavioural insights that enable the organization’s talent hiring and development efforts.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_i-win-startup-stories-how-lochan-helps-individuals-deal-with-their-career-related-dilemmas.txt'}), Document(page_content='Saumita is an Entrepreneur and a technology enthusiast with experience across Industrial R&D, Technology Analysis, and more recently, Book Publishing. column2: I-Venture @ ISB program?
column3:

column2: how i-venture assist startups in accessing funding and investment opportunities?
column3:
{'query': 'how i-venture assist startups in accessing funding and investment opportunities?', 'result': '
I-Venture @ ISB and Deshpande Startups have joined forces to run a pan India initiative to identify and engage potential entrepreneurs in the Agri and Food sector. This initiative aims to provide handholding, capacity building, and networking opportunities for startups to access funding and investment. ISB also has a Women of Innovation Program that provides acceleration support and a platform for fundraising for women-founded/co-founded startups. Additionally, I-Venture supports startups through its CleanTech Acceleration Program and facilitates the conversion of startups into profitable ventures. AIC also administers business incubators and provides support for entrepreneurship, as well as engages with the startup ecosystem in India. Finally, AIC offers support for startups in areas such as mentorship and business development, and also supports startups looking to expand globally.', 'source_documents': [Document(page_content='I-Venture @ ISB join forces with Deshpande Startups to run a pan India initiative to identify and engage an outstanding pool of potential entrepreneurs with innovative solutions to address problems in the Agri and Food sector with high growth potential. This initiative aims to build/nurture potential ventures by providing handholding, capacity building support, curated field visits to test/trial their products along with a platform to network with relevant stakeholders and investors.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_agrifood-accelerator.txt'}), Document(page_content='- "ISB has also been seeing some startups coming to the campus placement drives for recruitment."
 - "ISB is also doing an entrepreneurship programme under CM ST Entrepreneurship and Innovation (CMSTEI) scheme to support and promote entrepreneurs among scheduled tribes of Telangana."
 - "The Tribal Cooperative Finance Corporation (TRICOR) is the primary stakeholder in this programme."
 - "More than 170 startups graduated 70 raised funding Total funding raised by startups is about Rs 730 crore"', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_indian-school-of-business-to-create-global-corridor-for-startups.txt'}), Document(page_content='- I-Venture @ ISB’s Women of Innovation Program 
- provide acceleration support to women founded/co-founded start-ups 
- handholding entrepreneurs through their scaling-up journey 
- leveraging ISB’s strong network 
- enabling women to scale their products/services 
- Go-to-Market stage 
- scaling up through focused guidance, workshops, shared learning, networking 
- platform for fundraising 
- extensive business growth opportunities 
- I-WIN 2.0 
- investment ready 
- helpful for startups who want to raise funds in near future', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_iwin.txt'}), Document(page_content='Pitch Session  8 startups from India and the UK pitch to VCs', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_london-conference-2022.txt'}), Document(page_content='I-Venture @ISB, Kalaari Capital, Endiya Partners, T-Hub, ISB Hyderabad campus, I-Venture team, Professor Bhagwan Chowdhry, exchange ideas, make connections', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_i-connect-isb-creating-an-ecosystem-for-entrepreneurs-to-network.txt'}), Document(page_content='CleanTech Acceleration Program is specifically designed for startups incorporated in India. column2: i am a student and want to startup my venture. how can i-venture @ isb help?
column3: {'query': 'i am a student and want to startup my venture. how can i-venture @ isb help?', 'result': ' I-Venture @ ISB offers various resources and programs for students interested in starting their own ventures, including the I-WIN Accelerator program and the Tinkerpreneur bootcamp. They also provide opportunities for pitching to venture capitalists and networking with key stakeholders in the entrepreneurship ecosystem. column2: as a mentor or investor how can i be a part of i-venture
column3: {'query': 'as a mentor or investor how can i be a part of i-venture', 'result': ' As a mentor or investor, you can be a part of I-Venture @ ISB by joining forces with Deshpande Startups to run a pan India initiative to identify and engage potential entrepreneurs in the Agri and Food sector. You can also attend events and presentations at ISB to exchange ideas and make connections with other VCs and industry experts. Additionally, I-Venture @ ISB provides screening and selection of participants for their various programs, giving you the opportunity to mentor and invest in promising startups.', 'source_documents': [Document(page_content='I-Venture, which fosters entrepreneurship and nurtures startups at ISB. It administers business incubators and facilitates the conversion of startups into entrepreneurial ventures. It has various programmes that cater to ventures of all stages. “We have stepped up activities related to nurturing the entrepreneurship ecosystem.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_indian-school-of-business-to-create-global-corridor-for-startups.txt'}), Document(page_content='I-Venture @ISB, Kalaari Capital, Endiya Partners, T-Hub, ISB Hyderabad campus, I-Venture team, presentations, VCs, Professor Bhagwan Chowdhry, Faculty Director, exchange ideas, make connections.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_i-connect-isb-creating-an-ecosystem-for-entrepreneurs-to-network.txt'}), Document(page_content='Ms Vani Kola, Managing Director, Kalaari Capital; Mr Sateesh Andra, Managing Director, Endiya Partners; Mr Harkesh Mittal, Chairman, Startup India Seed Fund Committee; and Professor Madan Pillutla, Dean, ISB shared their insights at I-Connect@ISB. Speaking at the event, Dean Madan Pillutla said, “At ISB, we are creating an ecosystem to connect individuals and incubators which would not only help them, but also contribute to the nation’s growth.”\xa0\xa0 Ms Vani Kola said, “ISB has very special role to play. There’s a time and a place for what we can do in India in encouraging and exploring entrepreneurship to create meaningful value, not only for India but to be a beacon across the globe in the kind of the companies we create.” Mr Harkesh Mittal expressed that he sees a\xa0wonderful future as this is the time to be in India. “This is the time to be a startup, to be an investor and continue to be a startup ecosystem,” he said.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_i-connect-isb-creating-an-ecosystem-for-entrepreneurs-to-network.txt'}), Document(page_content='I-Venture @ ISB join forces with Deshpande Startups to run a pan India initiative to identify and engage an outstanding pool of potential entrepreneurs with innovative solutions to address problems in the Agri and Food sector with high growth potential.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_agrifood-accelerator.txt'}), Document(page_content='I-Venture @ ISB provides screening and selection of the participants, design and delivery of the academic training, facilitation of market exposures and financial exposure component of the programme for the selected set of 100 prospective entrepreneurs (2 cohorts of 50 participants each).', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_tricor.txt'})]}

column2: what is aic isb and dlabs?
column3:
{'query': 'what is aic isb and dlabs?', 'result': " AIC ISB and DLabs are innovation centers at the Indian School of Business (ISB) that support and accelerate innovations in AI, Blockchain, and DeFi. They provide a space for entrepreneurs to collaborate with mentors, investors, and academia, and contribute to the nation's growth.", 'source_documents': [Document(page_content='AIC ISB, DIRI, TRICOR', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_i-connect-isb.txt'}), Document(page_content='Lami.fit (lami.fit) is the perfect example of what happens when intuition, knowledge, experience and technology come together.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_i-win-startup-stories-in-a-world-where-fitness-is-measured-by-weight-alone-lami-fit-stands-out-by-a-mile.txt'}), Document(page_content='- That is what led to the genesis of OfExperiences, a platform that builds, develops and equips professionals who are undergoing career transitions by running niche cohort-based programs for them across career stages, and providing them with relevant information, personalized guidance, and real connections to help them navigate through their transitional phase. 
- OFExperiences also acts as a bridge between such professionals and organizations that are looking for similar talent. 
- Not only does Lochan’s brainchild help organizations with ready talent, but they also provide valuable behavioural insights that enable the organization’s talent hiring and development efforts. 
- For Lochan, giving shape to her dream has not been as easy as getting the idea itself. 
- It took some time to design the right business model and several experiments, market explorations and positioning exercises to get to the root of it all.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_i-win-startup-stories-how-lochan-helps-individuals-deal-with-their-career-related-dilemmas.txt'}), Document(page_content='About DLabs at the Indian School of Business (ISB) DLabs is the incubation and acceleration of ISB that hosts a state-of-the-art space for entrepreneurs to interact, engage and collaborate with mentors, investors and academia.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_build-for-billions-accelerator.txt'}), Document(page_content='Innovation Centres DLabs AIC ISB DIRI TRICOR Accelerating Innovations in AI, Blockchain and DeFi DLabs Incubator Association (DLabs) at the Indian School of Business (ISB)', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_finchain.txt'}), Document(page_content='- Professor Madan Pillutla, Dean, ISB shared their insights at I-Connect@ISB.

- Ms Vani Kola said, “ISB has very special role to play. There’s a time and a place for what we can do in India in encouraging and exploring entrepreneurship to create meaningful value, not only for India but to be a beacon across the globe in the kind of the companies we create.”
- Mr Harkesh Mittal expressed that he sees a wonderful future as this is the time to be in India.
- “This is the time to be a startup, to be an investor and continue to be a startup ecosystem,” he said.', metadata={'source': '/content/drive/MyDrive/striped_new/https___i-venture.org_i-connect-isb-creating-an-ecosystem-for-entrepreneurs-to-network.txt'})]}
